            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1526.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate approx. 250g&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[500g]</span>&nbsp;<strong>red cabbage</strong>&nbsp;(use the root as a handle and discard at the end!)</p>\r\n<p>Combine&nbsp;the&nbsp;<strong>grated red&nbsp;cabbage</strong>, <strong>mayonnaise</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>&nbsp;with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good old mix up &ndash; this is your <strong>red cabbage slaw&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
